Chordate:



Chordate chuckled softly, kissing Feline on the nose.  "It is a 
little warm in here.  And fresh air DOES sound good.  Just one sec."

He activated his comm. unit.  "Smokescreen, this is Chordate, come to 
the bridge and take over for me.  There's a Maximal waiting outside 
of the ship."

---

<Ok...> Smokescreen replied uncertain, leaving his post and heading 
for the bridge.

---

Chordate looked into Feline's beautiful optic sensors, giving her a 
final kiss.  "Alright.  I'll lead the way." he said, flashing a 
friendly smile, walking for the door, but at a pace that would take a 
few more cycles needed to get out of the Cybertronian Fire.
